jemalloc provides CMake targets:

    find_package(jemalloc CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE jemalloc::jemalloc)

Tebako fork features:
- Full ARM64 support on Windows (VS 2015-2022)
- musl libc support with ARM64 outline atomics fix
- Apple Silicon (macOS ARM64) support
- Comprehensive platform coverage via extensive CI
